title: Buck Satan 666 Shooters (Ministry) - Bikers Welcome (2011) (mp3)
description:
Buck Satan & The 666 Shooters -
"Bikers Welcome, Ladies Drink Free!" (2011) (320 kbps)

Curious side project of Al Jourgensen (the man behind Ministry, Lard, The Revolting Cocks, 1000 Homo DJs, Pigface - and many others), mixing country & western steel guitar, banjos, fiddles and harmonicas with Ministry's typical programmed drums, heavy guitar riffs and growled vocals.

Includes three cover versions - of tracks by The Greatful Dead, The Byrds, and Heartsfield.
